  "title": "Hex Casting Media Display (Teal's fork)",
  "description": "A mod that shows how much media you have in your inventory (in amethyst dust)",
  "body": "<center>\n<a href='https://fabricmc.net'><img alt=\"Supported on Fabric Loader\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://badger-api-staging.worldwidepixel.ca/cozy?gradientStart=dbd0b4&gradientEnd=aea694&lineOne=Supported%20on&lineTwo=Fabric%20Loader&colourOne=ffffff&colourTwo=dfdfa5&iconUrl=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/FabricMC/fabric-loader/refs/heads/master/src/main/resources/ui/icon/fabric_x128.png&format=svg\"></a>\n<a href='https://quiltmc.org'><img alt=\"Supported on Quilt Loader\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://badger-api-staging.worldwidepixel.ca/cozy?gradientStart=271f33&gradientEnd=1c1526&lineOne=Supported%20on&lineTwo=Quilt%20Loader&colourOne=ffffff&colourTwo=dc29dd&iconUrl=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/QuiltMC/quilt-loader/refs/heads/develop/src/main/resources/ui/icon/quilt_x128.png&format=svg\"></a>\n<a href='https://addons.hexxy.media'><img alt=\"Shown on Hex Casting Addons page\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://badger-api-staging.worldwidepixel.ca/cozy?gradientStart=3e3550&gradientEnd=2E2540&lineOne=Friend%20of&lineTwo=hexxy&colourOne=ffffff&colourTwo=BB89FA&iconUrl=https://hexxy.media/addons/hexfavicon.png&format=svg\"></a>\n</center>\n\nThis is a maintained fork of [Hexcasting Media Display](https://modrinth.com/mod/hexcasting-media-display) with some new features.\nThis fork was made with CarsonCoder's (the original author) permission.\n\nA mod that adds text above the hotbar that shows how much media you have in your inventory in units of amethyst dust. Useful for hex casting to know how much media you have so you don't die.\n\nMy version is meant to be easier on the eyes and fix some bugs. More will be added later though.",
